headline: ServiceNow and NTT DATA Expand Strategic Partnership to Accelerate AI-led Transformation for Global Enterprises
summary: SANTA CLARA, Calif. & LONDON, November 05, 2025--ServiceNow (NYSE: NOW), the AI platform for business transformation, and NTT DATA, a global leader in AI, digital business, and technology services, today announced an expanded strategic partnership to accelerate AI-led transformation for enterprises. The companies will execute joint go-to-market and delivery commitments, including co-developing and co-selling AI-powered solutions to help organizations to transform the way work gets done.
